# Design Factory skills directory — DEPRECATED (v49+).
#
# Phase E (commit baa0a03, 2026-04-24) used <repoRoot>/.claude/skills as
# the single source. v49 (2026-05-07) canonicalizes on
# <repoRoot>/skills/ — provider-agnostic, no Claude harness coupling.
#
# Compat behavior: the daemon walker reads BOTH paths. Canonical
# (/skills/) wins on (source, trigger) collision. Skills installed or
# edited via the app are written to /skills/ exclusively.
#
# To migrate any local skills:
#   mv .claude/skills/* skills/
#   rm -rf .claude/skills
#
# See docs/migration-skills.md for the full story.
